'''Michael (Mike) Phelps''' (born October 3, 1961, in [[Vicksburg, Mississippi]]) is a retired American professional [[basketball]] player. He attended [[Alcorn State University]] and was selected in the 7th round of the [[1985 NBA Draft]] by the [[Seattle SuperSonics]]. Phelps played with the Sonics and [[Los Angeles Clippers]].
